---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About | Justin Hoffmann">
  <section class="container">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <p>
      I'm a Systems Administrator with a passion for building reliable,
      secure, and efficient IT infrastructure. I enjoy solving technical
      problems, learning new technologies, and creating home lab projects
      that help me grow professionally.
    </p>

    <h2>What I Do</h2>

    <p>
      In my day-to-day work, I support business environments using Microsoft
      365, Entra ID, Windows systems, networking, and endpoint management.
      I enjoy troubleshooting complex issues and finding long-term solutions
      rather than temporary fixes.
    </p>

    <h2>My Home Lab</h2>

    <p>
      Outside of work, I maintain a Proxmox-based home lab where I experiment
      with virtualization, Docker containers, networking, automation, and
      self-hosted services. It allows me to explore enterprise technologies
      in a hands-on environment and continuously improve my skills.
    </p>

    <h2>Currently Learning</h2>

    <p>
      I'm continually expanding my knowledge in networking, automation,
      Linux administration, and infrastructure technologies. I believe the
      best way to learn is by building real projects and documenting the
      process.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
  }

  h1 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #cfcfcf;
  }
</style>